(9, 1, '2017-09-20 21:05:04', '2017-09-20 21:05:04', '<p class="font_8">My name is Milivoj Vasi<span style="font-size: 1rem;">ljevic  and I am professional </span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">photographer.  I was born in 1983. in city of Pančevo, Serbia.</span></p>\r\n<p class="font_8">I started six years ago when I visited, probably first photo exhibition in my life. Three days later I visited same exhibition again and that was it. It was a love at first sight. I bought my first camera, finished first photography course, got my first friends photographers… And that was it, I became photographer in a thirty days  .</p>\r\n<p class="font_8">Next year, in 2009, I became a member of the amateur photo club "CFFKS"  and the Photo Association of Serbia. Then the real magic started. At that moment CFFKS was probably the best place for photography in region, it was a real center for photography with more than 30 active photographers  of a different skills and styles, but with a same, great enthusiasm and passion for photography.  On waves of that energy I made my first, I feel free to say, great shots and not long after I won my first awards on photo salons we were competing in .</p>\r\n<p class="font_8">Since then I won several awards on domestic and international photo salons, my photos have been published many times in several magazines. From 2010 I am volunteer photographer at Art of living Foundation, Serbia.</p>\r\n<p class="font_8">On 14th April 2013, I had my first solo exhibition "The First Horisons", in Ivanovo, Serbia.\r\nDuring 2014 i was lucky to work for more than 7 months as a photographer on Royal Princess,  one of the greatest cruise ships on planet.</p>\r\n<p class="font_8">Through my photos I\'m trying to tell you all my good intentions I have for people, nature, life. I hope you like how I do it .</p>\r\n<p class="font_8"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-10" style="font-size: 1rem;" src="http://wordpress-milivoj.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/milivoj-186x300.jpg" alt="" width="186" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p class="font_8">Good light</p>', 'Milivoj Vasiljevic - Behind the lens', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'milivoj-vasiljevic-behind-the-lens', '', '', '2017-09-20 21:05:04', '2017-09-20 21:05:04', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-milivoj.dev/?p=9', 0, 'post', '', 0),
